base (hardening, encryption, segregation, audit logs, retention policy)

     *   Answer: SQL is protected by Azure security and includes automatic =
patching and firewalls. Event logging on all databases. Danelec Terms om Co=
nditions specifies 3 years of Telemetry data retention.

Backup & Business Continuity

